ops::bit::BitOrAssign::bitor_assign.doc:
Performs the `|=` operation.

# Examples

```
let mut x = true;
x |= false;
assert_eq!(x, true);

let mut x = false;
x |= false;
assert_eq!(x, false);

let mut x: u8 = 5;
x |= 1;
assert_eq!(x, 5);

let mut x: u8 = 5;
x |= 2;
assert_eq!(x, 7);
```

